name: BM #1 Curio 17
description:
This is the first NFT made by Blockchain Museum.

This Art Piece represents the first Doge on Ethereum and other two historical moments, the first Bitcoin fork, which was intended to be represented by the Curio #17 card, and the "release mistake" of Curio #17 card which made this card the only Curio Card with a "B" version.
